132
00:09:10.050 --> 00:09:11.541
Jack.

133
00:09:11.584 --> 00:09:13.644
Jack. tell me what you know.

134
00:09:13.686 --> 00:09:15.314
I fucked up. man. Yeah?

135
00:09:15.555 --> 00:09:17.251
I-I should've... What happened?

136
00:09:17.290 --> 00:09:19.759
