139
00:09:24.164 --> 00:09:26.656
Kids. Kids.

140
00:09:26.699 --> 00:09:28.600
Fucking nobodies. man.

141
00:09:28.635 --> 00:09:30.661
Fucking nobodies.

142
00:09:30.703 --> 00:09:32.069
In some...

143
00:09:32.105 --> 00:09:34.665
