144
00:09:34.707 --> 00:09:35.707
red Nova.

145
00:09:35.742 --> 00:09:38.211
Mm-hmm?

146
00:09:38.244 --> 00:09:42.113
Yes?

147
00:09:42.148 --> 00:09:44.845
G-4...

148
00:09:44.884 --> 00:09:47.649
4-3...

149
00:09:47.687 --> 00:09:50.122
