152
00:10:02.769 --> 00:10:04.704
We should leave.

153
00:10:04.737 --> 00:10:07.764
Should we leave? Darren?

154
00:10:07.807 --> 00:10:08.775
All right. I don't know.

155
00:10:08.808 --> 00:10:10.834
Okay?

156
00:10:10.877 --> 00:10:12.869
Look. they have
to know it was us.

157
00:10:12.912 --> 00:10:14.472
And if they don't by
now. your dad will.

158
00:10:14.614 --> 00:10:17.812
