178
00:11:28.021 --> 00:11:29.922
Fuck!

179
00:11:29.956 --> 00:11:32.755
Where's your fucking brother?!

180
00:11:32.792 --> 00:11:34.920
'Cause I heard he had
a fucking pistol on him

181
00:11:34.961 --> 00:11:36.190
and he and my boy went

182
00:11:36.229 --> 00:11:38.698
and put a bullet in
some Albanian nobody.

183
00:11:38.731 --> 00:11:40.393
Now I ain't seen either since.

184
00:11:40.433 --> 00:11:41.901
But I know they're not in hiding

185
00:11:41.935 --> 00:11:44.370
'cause of some
fucking dead Albanian.

186
00:11:44.404 --> 00:11:46.236
I swear to God! I
don't know anything!

187
00:11:46.272 --> 00:11:48.173
Well. that makes two of us now.

188
00:11:48.208 --> 00:11:49.437
Dad!

189
00:11:49.475 --> 00:11:51.740
[Breathing heavily]

190
00:11:55.815 --> 00:11:58.717
loan. He asked if
he could borrow her.

191
00:11:58.751 --> 00:12:00.162
I swear to God. Kinney.
I don't know anything.

192
00:12:00.186 --> 00:12:01.186
So please don't!

193
00:12:01.221 --> 00:12:02.484
Find 'em!

194
00:12:02.722 --> 00:12:03.917
Both of 'em!

195
00:12:27.513 --> 00:12:30.779
I want Luan right
here. on his knees.

196
00:12:30.817 --> 00:12:32.183
