looking for his killer.

203
00:12:45.064 --> 00:12:47.829
We are making enemies
out of business partners.

204
00:12:47.867 --> 00:12:50.803
And the longer that goes
on. the sooner they turn on us.

205
00:12:50.837 --> 00:12:54.274
We've got to find a
peaceful solution to this.

206
00:12:54.307 --> 00:12:57.436
Did you see my
dad's face in there?

207
00:12:57.477 --> 00:13:00.538
I'm not interested in peace.

208
00:13:05.485 --> 00:13:08.284
Marian. talk to your boy.

209
00:13:10.123 --> 00:13:12.558
I agree with Sean.

210
00:13:12.792 --> 00:13:17.821
Whoever killed my husband
remains an enemy to this family.

211
00:13:17.864 --> 00:13:20.265
If we back down now.
they'll walk all over us.

212
00:13:20.300 --> 00:13:22.895
