- En... Enough!

213
00:13:22.935 --> 00:13:24.528
All of you.

214
00:13:24.570 --> 00:13:28.268
Our strength lies in our unity.

215
00:13:28.308 --> 00:13:30.539
That's what your
dad built for us.

216
00:13:35.815 --> 00:13:38.375
[Sighs]

217
00:13:38.418 --> 00:13:41.149
Listen. son.

218
00:13:41.187 --> 00:13:43.520
I want nothing more
than to bring you the head

219
00:13:43.556 --> 00:13:49.462
