the guts to do this to us.

220
00:13:49.495 --> 00:13:55.127
But. in that meeting. this
morning. you acted alone.

221
00:13:55.168 --> 00:13:58.866
And that makes us
look weak and divided.

222
00:13:58.905 --> 00:14:02.137
Work with me. Sean.
and I promise you

223
00:14:02.175 --> 00:14:05.407
I will give you everything.

224
00:14:05.445 --> 00:14:10.179
just like I did for your father.

225
00:14:10.216 --> 00:14:12.151
I'm glad to hear it.

226
00:14:12.185 --> 00:14:13.462
[Indistinct shouting
in distance]

227
00:14:13.486 --> 00:14:14.977
