228
00:14:15.021 --> 00:14:16.614
- No fucking way!
- Jack!

229
00:14:16.856 --> 00:14:18.167
Take your fucking
hands off him now!

230
00:14:18.191 --> 00:14:19.591
Jack! Get him in the boardroom!

231
00:14:19.625 --> 00:14:24.029
- Watch out.
- I'm so fucking sorry.

232
00:14:24.063 --> 00:14:25.463
Get him outside! No. no.

233
00:14:25.498 --> 00:14:27.126
He stays.

234
00:14:27.166 --> 00:14:29.397
Come on. Jack.

235
00:14:29.435 --> 00:14:31.097
Come on. Jack. It's
okay. Get a doctor.

236
00:14:31.137 --> 00:14:33.470
Get a doctor! Come on. Jack.

237
00:14:33.506 --> 00:14:34.633
Come on. Jack.

238
00:14:34.874 --> 00:14:36.467
Come on. Jack. It's okay.

239
00:14:36.509 --> 00:14:38.000
[Indistinct conversations]

240
00:14:38.044 --> 00:14:40.445
Where have you been? Jack?

241
00:14:40.480 --> 00:14:42.574
- Sean.
- Give him some space.

242
00:14:42.615 --> 00:14:46.052
No. no. no. Jack.
No. no. no. no. No.

243
00:14:46.085 --> 00:14:47.883
Fuck!

244
00:14:47.920 --> 00:14:51.948
