245
00:14:51.991 --> 00:14:53.435
How's he doing in
there? He passed out.

246
00:14:53.459 --> 00:14:55.189
Yeah. he does that a lot.

247
00:14:55.228 --> 00:14:57.005
- Who the fuck are you?
- It's okay. He's one of ours.

248
00:14:57.029 --> 00:14:58.273
He's the twat that
tore up the pub.

249
00:14:58.297 --> 00:15:00.129
Elliot.

250
00:15:00.166 --> 00:15:01.998
I'm the one who found him.

251
00:15:02.034 --> 00:15:03.900
And you did all of
that on your own?

252
00:15:03.936 --> 00:15:05.564
What was it? Six of them?

253
00:15:05.605 --> 00:15:08.473
Eight. But I had a dart. so...

254
00:15:08.508 --> 00:15:10.272
♪♪

255
00:15:10.309 --> 00:15:11.309
Come on.

256
00:15:11.344 --> 00:15:19.344
♪♪

257
00:15:21.020 --> 00:15:22.511
